# Gold Shop Management System

A Django-based backend web application for managing inventory in a gold shop.  
Built with Django and Django REST Framework.

---

## üöÄ Features

- User Authentication (Login / Logout)
- Role-based Access (Manager / Staff)
- Inventory CRUD Operations
- Dashboard with Statistics
- REST API Endpoints
- Clean UI with reusable templates

---

## üõ† Tech Stack

- Python
- Django
- Django REST Framework
- SQLite (Development)
- HTML / CSS

---

## üì° API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|------------|
| GET | /api/inventory/ | List all items |
| POST | /api/inventory/ | Create new item |
| GET | /api/inventory/{id}/ | Retrieve item |
| PUT | /api/inventory/{id}/ | Update item |
| DELETE | /api/inventory/{id}/ | Delete item |

